2 CONC arcia descended another Joseph Garcia, from the second Joseph Garcia I descend Miguel Garcia the Groom, and from Isabel Garcia descended Joaquin de Cepeda, from Joaquin de Cepeda descended Isabel de Cepeda the Bride......</transcription></metadatax
