2 TITL Antonio Camargo & Maria Marcela Rangel Marriage 2 Jul 1748 Galeana.
1 _OID f59214b1-7e6b-421b-a56a-b6ce027140b1
1 DATE 2 Jul 1748
1 PLAC Galeana, Nuevo Leon, Mexico
1 _DSCR Marriage Document (Bottom Left & Top Right Pages)
1 _META <metadataxml><transcription>On 2 July 1748, in this Parish Church de San Pablo de los Labradores, the Marriage of Antonio Camargo (Yndio) Native Indian originally from Queretaro and a resident in this jurisdiction for 3 years, widowed of Barthola d
2 CONC e SanJuan (India) Native Indian for about 11 years here in this area, with Marcela Rangel Mestiza and neighbor of this Valle, widower of Juan de Gauna who is been deceased for 2 years in this part, both are neighbors of this Valle, Best man Josep
2 CONC h Domingo Melo and Maid of honor his wife Maria Pondiana, witnesses were Geronimo Montes, Joseph Jimenez, and Pedro de Castro, and for the record I sign it Fray Gonzalo Diaz Cardona.</transcription></metadataxml>
